title: Behind The Art With Jimbo Phillips
description: It's definitely a family affair over at Phillips Studios. Jimbo Phillips talks about the new decks he drew for Emmanuel Guzman, Justin Strubing, Sid Melvin and Shuriken Shannon in honor of Santa Cruz's 40th Anniversary.
